name: hv_return_t
desc: The return type of framework functions.

items.name: var HV_BUSY: Int
items.desc: The operation was unsuccessful because the owning resource was busy.

items.name: var HV_BAD_ARGUMENT: Int
items.desc: The operation was unsuccessful because the function call had an invalid argument.

items.name: var HV_NO_RESOURCES: Int
items.desc: The operation was unsuccessful because the host had no resources available to complete the request.

items.name: var HV_NO_DEVICE: Int
items.desc: The operation was unsuccessful because no VM or vCPU was available.
